rams.</strong></p>\n<p>Key Features:</p>\n<p>🔮 Mystical Intricacy: With its elaborate design and fine details, this model beckons you to explore the unknown.</p>\n<p>📸 PBR Textures: Exceptional PBR texture sets bring out the hand-crafted quality, making the board and planchette almost lifelike.</p>\n<p>🌍 Spiritual Aesthetics: The moth centerpiece adds an extra layer of symbolism and beauty, elevating the model’s spiritual allure.</p>\n<p>🌌 Versatile Use: Perfect for mystical narratives, horror scenes, or even integration into real-time game engines.</p>\n<p>Do you dare to seek answers from the other side? Add this ornate Ouija board and planchette to your collection and let the spirits guide you!</p>","isAiForbidden":false,"isAiGenerated":false,"lastUpdatedAt":"","listingType":"3d-model","media":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/ab1d8d75-8382-4d7b-bbea-5a8b76d993a7/4553fe19-6bf6-43e4-8276-fa4fff6c37d6.jpeg","publishedAt":"2024-10-05T00:27:24.906144Z","reviewCount":3,"thumbnail":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/10598f70-13dc-49bc-b4aa-aae0747f43a9/bef91fbf-7305-4fad-ab94-9bb6b6e66f3c.jpeg","title":"Ornate Ouija Board and Planchette","uid":"d331a169-0405-44e5-8280-83e009c635cd","updatedAt":"","user":{"coverImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-65q3mn6k9ws4szh7h8dq39272qbqtt/cover/6acb2c20.png","profileImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-65q3mn6k9ws4szh7h8dq39272qbqtt/profileImage/blob-500x500-002d54c6574722549ab9ee47c85fefd2.jpg","sellerName":"Glowbox3D","uid":"20891416-4d7f-4c66-b18c-9ba2979d955c"},"tags":[{"name":"Demon","slug":"demon","uid":"029e2063-bbdc-41fd-b130-3029e4bb2462"},{"name":"Halloween","slug":"halloween","uid":"6336c3a7-4460-4ee8-9b64-f55407388901"},{"name":"Ghost","slug":"ghost","uid":"64948d91-330c-4517-a4fc-8961f9b98d32"},{"name":"Photorealistic","slug":"photorealistic","uid":"7485c72b-1f18-499f-8c65-0fdf1e2a21d0"},{"name":"Scary","slug":"scary","uid":"a08d047a-382f-498a-a278-f87aa4